```{r pancreas 32253675, include=FALSE}

PMID_32253675 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32253675', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32253675 <- paste0(PMID_32253675$journal,' ', PMID_32253675$year, ' ', PMID_32253675$month,';', PMID_32253675$volume,'(', PMID_32253675$number,'):', PMID_32253675$pages)

PubMed_32253675 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32253675$eprint)

doi_32253675 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32253675$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
